{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Mr Zhang Blog","author":"Mark Zhang"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"3875ac84-b67c-5be9-8466-cf0b07430fda","excerpt":"最近事儿比较多，一直没时间写东西，前几天又遇到关于获取元素大小的问题，每次遇到这类问题就翻书，比较费时间，所以总结一下。 1.元素的偏移量 元素的偏移量包括元素在屏幕上占用的所有可见的空间。元素的可见大小由其高度、宽度决定，包括所有内边距、滚动条和边框大小（注意：这里并不包括外边距）。…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>最近事儿比较多，一直没时间写东西，前几天又遇到关于获取元素大小的问题，每次遇到这类问题就翻书，比较费时间，所以总结一下。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3>1.元素的偏移量</h3>\n<p>元素的偏移量包括元素在屏幕上占用的所有可见的空间。元素的可见大小由其高度、宽度决定，包括所有内边距、滚动条和边框大小（注意：这里并不包括外边距）。</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/home/static/b8cea7adfbc3e662190f03377879ffc3/f9336/offset_table.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 18.78980891719745%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"icon\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/blog/home/static/b8cea7adfbc3e662190f03377879ffc3/6255c/offset_table.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/home/static/b8cea7adfbc3e662190f03377879ffc3/375dc/offset_table.png 148w,\n/blog/home/static/b8cea7adfbc3e662190f03377879ffc3/6b157/offset_table.png 295w,\n/blog/home/static/b8cea7adfbc3e662190f03377879ffc3/6255c/offset_table.png 590w,\n/blog/home/static/b8cea7adfbc3e662190f03377879ffc3/dcf9c/offset_table.png 885w,\n/blog/home/static/b8cea7adfbc3e662190f03377879ffc3/f9336/offset_table.png 942w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<!--more-->\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/home/static/4a705a961a82c8193ab277a6519714cf/c747b/offset.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 59.19117647058824%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"icon\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/blog/home/static/4a705a961a82c8193ab277a6519714cf/6255c/offset.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/home/static/4a705a961a82c8193ab277a6519714cf/375dc/offset.png 148w,\n/blog/home/static/4a705a961a82c8193ab277a6519714cf/6b157/offset.png 295w,\n/blog/home/static/4a705a961a82c8193ab277a6519714cf/6255c/offset.png 590w,\n/blog/home/static/4a705a961a82c8193ab277a6519714cf/c747b/offset.png 816w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h3>2.客户区大小</h3>\n<p>元素的客户区大小指的是元素内容机器内边距占据空间的大小。</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/home/static/ca2a47e4e2976c2855163f0d6850e9f8/9ec89/client_table.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 11.501597444089457%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAdUlEQVQI102N2w6CMBBE+f/Pk6BEjfRFHiBBKk23pZejy4Nxk5PZ7Exmm5wz4j3j+ER3xa4rzjlyyb+bEmNERJinmRDCQfrzU0o0pRS294Z5GLwXdF7LgrWWWusRVN33yKXvObUtw2C436503ZnwfaK+9mj2AxfAmjCghTVqAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"icon\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/blog/home/static/ca2a47e4e2976c2855163f0d6850e9f8/6255c/client_table.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/home/static/ca2a47e4e2976c2855163f0d6850e9f8/375dc/client_table.png 148w,\n/blog/home/static/ca2a47e4e2976c2855163f0d6850e9f8/6b157/client_table.png 295w,\n/blog/home/static/ca2a47e4e2976c2855163f0d6850e9f8/6255c/client_table.png 590w,\n/blog/home/static/ca2a47e4e2976c2855163f0d6850e9f8/dcf9c/client_table.png 885w,\n/blog/home/static/ca2a47e4e2976c2855163f0d6850e9f8/9ec89/client_table.png 939w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/home/static/3010402370455b3ff800d07493a4af5d/5f03a/client.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.55263157894737%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"icon\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/blog/home/static/3010402370455b3ff800d07493a4af5d/6255c/client.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/home/static/3010402370455b3ff800d07493a4af5d/375dc/client.png 148w,\n/blog/home/static/3010402370455b3ff800d07493a4af5d/6b157/client.png 295w,\n/blog/home/static/3010402370455b3ff800d07493a4af5d/6255c/client.png 590w,\n/blog/home/static/3010402370455b3ff800d07493a4af5d/5f03a/client.png 760w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>要确定浏览器可见窗口的大小，可以使用<code class=\"language-text\">document.documentElement</code>或<code class=\"language-text\">document.body</code>（IE7之前的版本中）。</p>\n<p>从以上两个我们可以看出元素偏移量（offset）与客户区大小（client）的区别在于<strong>有没有包含边框</strong>，客户区大小不包含边框。</p>\n<h3>3.滚动大小</h3>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/home/static/e0b52f068584f2dd8dd149783740fafd/f9336/scroll_table.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 18.577494692144374%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"icon\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/blog/home/static/e0b52f068584f2dd8dd149783740fafd/6255c/scroll_table.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/home/static/e0b52f068584f2dd8dd149783740fafd/375dc/scroll_table.png 148w,\n/blog/home/static/e0b52f068584f2dd8dd149783740fafd/6b157/scroll_table.png 295w,\n/blog/home/static/e0b52f068584f2dd8dd149783740fafd/6255c/scroll_table.png 590w,\n/blog/home/static/e0b52f068584f2dd8dd149783740fafd/dcf9c/scroll_table.png 885w,\n/blog/home/static/e0b52f068584f2dd8dd149783740fafd/f9336/scroll_table.png 942w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">scrollWidth</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">scrollHeight</code>主要用于确定元素内容的实际大小。所以带有垂直滚动条的页面总高度就是<code class=\"language-text\">document.documentElement.scrollHeight</code>。</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/home/static/7958c58174a608ed2cbd97d165a4ff28/e5dbf/scroll.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 61.141304347826086%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"icon\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/blog/home/static/7958c58174a608ed2cbd97d165a4ff28/6255c/scroll.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/home/static/7958c58174a608ed2cbd97d165a4ff28/375dc/scroll.png 148w,\n/blog/home/static/7958c58174a608ed2cbd97d165a4ff28/6b157/scroll.png 295w,\n/blog/home/static/7958c58174a608ed2cbd97d165a4ff28/6255c/scroll.png 590w,\n/blog/home/static/7958c58174a608ed2cbd97d165a4ff28/dcf9c/scroll.png 885w,\n/blog/home/static/7958c58174a608ed2cbd97d165a4ff28/e5dbf/scroll.png 1104w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h3>4.窗口大小</h3>\n<p>在现代主流浏览器中提供了四个属性确定窗口的大小，分别为：<code class=\"language-text\">innerWidth</code>、<code class=\"language-text\">innerHeight</code>、<code class=\"language-text\">outerWidth</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">outerHeight</code>。</p>\n<h4>4.1. outerWidth和outerHeight</h4>\n<p>返回浏览器窗口本身的尺寸（无论是从外层的window对象还是从某个框架访问）</p>\n<h4>4.2. innerWidth和innerHeight</h4>\n<p>返回该容器中页面试图去的大小（减去边框宽度）</p>\n<p><strong>注意：</strong></p>\n<p>这里在《javascript高级程序设计》（第三版）中写道在chrome中outer与inner返回的值是一样的，这算是chrome的一个bug，我在chrome 53中已经修复，但是在QQ浏览器中（内核为chromium47）依旧是相等的，这需要注意！\n<code class=\"language-text\">clientWidth</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">clientHeight</code>。</p>\n<p>在主流浏览器中，<code class=\"language-text\">document.docuementElement.clientWidth</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">document.documentElement.clientHeight</code>中保存的是页面视口信息。返回的值与<code class=\"language-text\">window.innerHeight</code>，<code class=\"language-text\">window.innerWidth</code>一样。\n但是<code class=\"language-text\">window.innerHeight</code>在IE8及以下浏览器中结果是<code class=\"language-text\">undefined</code>，而<code class=\"language-text\">document.documentElement.clientHeight</code>还有值。所以在各个浏览器下取得页面视口大小的代码如下：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> pageWidth<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerWidth<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    pageHeight<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHeight<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">typeof</span> pageWidth <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> <span class=\"token string\">'number'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>compatMode <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">'CSS1Compat'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        pageWidth<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>documentElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>clientWidth<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        pageHeight<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>documentElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>clientHeight<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token keyword\">else</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        pageWidth<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>body<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>clientWidth<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        pageHeight<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>body<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>clientHeight<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>    </code></pre></div>\n<p>代码中<code class=\"language-text\">document.compatMode</code>用于判断浏览器处于什么模式，它有两个值：\n<code class=\"language-text\">BackCompat</code>:浏览器处于怪异模式\n<code class=\"language-text\">CSS1Compat</code>:浏览器处于标准模式\n不同模式下，获取浏览器的宽度的方法不同，在代码中已经做了判断。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"JS中的位置与大小","date":"August 03, 2016"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/2016-jsPosition/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2016-jsArray/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Javascript中Array方法的总结"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2016-jsString/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Javascript中字符串方法总结"}}}}